# Xcode
#
# gitignore contributors: remember to update Global/Xcode.gitignore, Objective-C.gitignore & Swift.gitignore

## User settings
xcuserdata/

## Xcode 8 and earlier
*.xcuserstate
*.xcscmblueprint

## Xcode 13 and later
.swiftpm/xcode/package.xcworkspace/contents.xcworkspacedata
.swiftpm/xcode/xcuserdata/

## Build artifacts
build/
DerivedData/

## Project settings
!default.pbxuser
!default.mode1v3
!default.mode2v3
!default.perspectivev3

## Error logs
*.mode1v3
*.mode2v3
*.perspectivev3
*.xccheckout

## Swift Package Manager
.build/
.swiftpm/
# If you want to cache dependencies, comment the line below
Packages/

## CocoaPods
# It is often recommended to include Pods/ in git, 
# but if you prefer to exclude it, uncomment the next line:
# Pods/

## Carthage
Carthage/Build/

## Fastlane
fastlane/report.xml
fastlane/Preview.html
fastlane/screenshots
fastlane/test_output

## Other
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.lock
